Class BMLSyncPoint

java.lang.Object

      de.dfki.embots.bml.sync.BMLSyncPoint
Direct Known Subclasses:
BMLRelativeSyncPoint, BMLSpeechSyncPoint, BMLVirtualSyncPoint
public class BMLSyncPoint
extends BMLElement

Sync points can be one of the standard BML sync points (start, ready, stroke_start etc.) or a specifically defined time point in the speech stream (with ). For the standard sync points the ID corresponds to the sync label ("start", "ready" etc.).
